entries.s_10: You have performed your tasks well.
entries.s_14: Please speak to Kiki about the successful resolution of the tasks I have asked of you.
entries.s_15: You are a friend to the den and always welcome here.
entries.s_16: Please resume your efforts, else we have nothing to discuss.
entries.s_18: The other have you involved in tasks that they think will help us against the smugglers. The most important way we can escape their control, however is to get our den mates back.
entries.s_20: They have abducted some of your people?
entries.s_22: Correct. The other tasks will help us, but return of our people is paramount. Could you please inspect the smuggler base and look for our den mates?
entries.s_26: Thank you. Here are the locations of the buildings I wish you to inspect.
entries.s_28: You have no business with us, outsider.
entries.s_9: You have not performed the task I have requested, have you?
